OOC: Oops.  Who's pod was it again?

::Pyrotaur/Terrataur::
       Pyrotaur looks at Windlord.  "I suppose Terrataur should be there by 
now.  I wouldn't worry too much.

       Terrataur arrived at the pod.  She looked at the controls and sent a 
message to Windlord.  "Do you want the whole pod or should I wake them up 
here?"
